---
title: Tofu and Corn Chowder with Green Onions
description: This chowder is made for chilly winter nights—and it's calling your name! Tofu and corn are the stars of the show in this big bowl of goodness, while a touch of jalapeño kicks up the flavour. Time to get cozy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-and-corn-chowder-f8203855-25a073c3.jpg
